title: DDFP 340: Bucky Brooks & Michael Robinson
itunes:title: DDFP 340: Bucky Brooks & Michael Robinson
description:
Shek is joined by former NFL scout Bucky Brooks to review his latest NFL.com mock draft, discuss Marcus Mariota's competitive nature and Jameis Winston's impact on the the NFC South if drafted by the Buccaneers. The guys also discuss the NFL's most versatile quarterbacks. Lastly, an update on #DDFP bracketology and Michael Robinson discusses the Seahawks' offseason.
